results.description: Not sure what kind of bird this was; I am still going through old trip photos from the past. This guy was one of the first birds I encountered at Ink's Lake. It was a tan/yellow bird with a little white and a mask. it was hidden in the sticks and I was not able to get any other photos before I moved on after he flew off.
